	<Task>
		<Title>Cleanup old console caches - Windows</Title>
		<Description><![CDATA[&lt;enter a description of the task here&gt; ]]></Description>
		<Relevance>windows of operating system</Relevance>
		<Relevance><![CDATA[exists (now - it) whose(it > 15*day) of modification times of folders of folders "AppData\Local\BigFix\Enterprise Console" of folders of folders "C:\Users"]]></Relevance>
		<Category></Category>
		<DownloadSize>0</DownloadSize>
		<Source>Internal</Source>
